y students faculty and advisors academic calendar explore degrees explore courses axess office of the registrar undergraduate academic life the stanford undergraduate program is designed to achieve balance between depth of knowledge acquired through specialization and breadth of knowledge gained through exploration undergraduate academic life graduate academic life while responsibility for graduate studies lies primarily with stanford's departments and schools the vice provost for graduate education works across the university to enhance the quality of graduate education vice provost for graduate education professional continuing & k 12 stanford offers valuable opportunities for lifelong learning including continuing adult education executive and professional programs and special programs for k 12 students continuing studies scpd stanford online exec ed business exec ed law summer session program for gifted youth complete listing see also stanford university libraries more than twenty libraries eight million volumes and extensive online collections stanford on itunes u download stanford courses faculty lectures interviews and more for your ipod or computer stanford on youtube stanford on youtube includes hundreds of videos from classes and campus events jobs make a gift emergency info search contact us about this site accreditation stanford university stanford california 94305 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints
